optionsTabBackreativKup.description: Appears in Options as a tab header for options related to saving/restoring your settings. To fit inside the button, it should not be longer than ~20-25 characters (depending on their width).

optionsTabAdvanced.description: Appears in Options as a tab header for advanced/niche options. To fit inside the button, it should not be longer than ~20-25 characters (depending on their width).
